    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，工单层到组件层。那Part1和Part2都指向同一个MRO编码吗？我看你写的是MRO250100001，Part3单独走MRO250100002？",
