    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，Part1和Part2共用同一个物料MRO250100001，Part3用MRO250100002。然后这两个物料都入库到库存节点S。",
      "elements_involved": [
